results.title: Mark of the Mutant!
results.description: Firestar manifests her powers for the first time.  Her Grandmother dies, which triggers the manifestation.  She is recruited by the White Queen.

results.title: The Players and the Pawn!
results.description: Tells about Firestar's life at the White Queen's school.  She meets the Hellions.  She meets the New Mutants.  The White Queen strengthens her control over Firestar's mind.

results.title: This Lady Kills!
results.description: The White Queen prepares Firestar to Assassinate the Black Queen.

results.title: Now Strikes the Assassin!
results.description: Firestar realizes what that the White Queen is evil, and turns on her.

results.title: The Way of the Samurai is Found in Death
results.description: Shield hires Elektra to cut through Hydra and kill the leader of Iraq.

results.title: Unemployment
results.description: Elektra romps around New York in her own particular idiom.

results.title: [Introspect Part 1]
results.description: Elektra desperately looks for work but ends up being found by Mr. Locke.

results.title: Introspect Part 2
results.description: Locke explains to a drugged up Elektra that she is nothing but a killer who deals death to the guilty and the innocent alike; One of the innocents turned out to be his girlfriend and for that, Locke drops her off in the middle of the Mojave Desert to die.

results.title: Introspect Part 3
results.description: Elektra wanders the Mojave desert in a stupor; The Coalition of Elektra's victims are livid with Locke for letting her go; When the gang goes out to search for Elektra, they find her passed out and suffering from a rattlesnake bite.
